    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "\n\nI gave the #b#t4031011##k to #p102# in #m10000000# and received the #b#t4031009##k in return. Now, all I need to do is get this to #b#p207##k, and I'm done, but the more I think about it, the more I regret saying yes. Anyway, this medicine looks quite tasty. If I ever find myself thirsty and without any water, maybe I should just drink it myself. Hahaha..."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I went back to #m10001000# and handed #p207# the weird medicine. Hopefully, she'll get better after taking this. As a sign of thanks, #p207# gave me 5,000 mesos and a #b#t1002081##k. This hat... I mean, it looks like it's going to help when I'm walking under a blazing sun, but it looks so old and raggedy... and if I put it on, it makes this weird noise, and it feels like insects are moving around inside it... am I going to be alright...?"
    }
  },
